verses.psalm:
DEAL BOUNTIFULLY WITH THY SERVANT;
GIVE ME LIFE, AND I SHALL KEEP THY
WORD. (v. 17)

MY SOUL MELTS AWAY FOR SORROW;
STRENGTHEN ME ACCORDING TO THY
WORD. (v. 28)

verses.troparion:
One Person of the Godhead,
for the sake of mortal men,
endures a shameful death on the cross;
the sun trembles and the earth quakes in
fear.

verses.psalm:
I ENTREAT THY FAVOR WITH ALL MY HEART;
BE MERCIFUL TO ME ACCORDING TO THY
PROMISE. (v. 58)

I HAVE DONE WHAT IS JUST AND RIGHT;
DO NOT LEAVE ME TO MY OPPRESSORS.
(v. 121)

GREAT ARE THY TENDER MERCIES, O LORD;
GIVE ME LIFE ACCORDING TO THY JUSTICE.
(v. 156)

LET MY CRY COME BEFORE THEE, O LORD;
GIVE ME UNDERSTANDING ACCORDING
TO THY WORD! (v. 169)

LET MY SUPPLICATION COME BEFORE THEE;
DELIVER ME ACCORDING TO THY WORD.
(v. 170)
